cast.overview: Marcus and Mike are forced to confront new threats, career changes, and midlife crises as they join the newly created elite team AMMO of the Miami police department to take down the ruthless Armando Armas, the vicious leader of a Miami drug cartel.
cast.title: Bad Boys for Life

details.biography:
Rory Markham (born March 25, 1982) is an American professional mixed martial artist, stuntman and actor who most recently competed in the Middleweight division. A professional competitor since 2003 Markham has formerly competed for the UFC and the IFL, representing the Quad Cities Silverbacks.

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
